{"id": 1902, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪一种类型的漫画读者？", "description": "你还看漫画吗？现在你都上哪儿看漫画？(题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 7538, "comment_count": 40, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170912173555gO8HxI96j5if1Ayb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-13T17:00:30Z", "questions": [{"id": 2958, "title": "你是哪一种类型的漫画读者？", "content": "你是哪一种类型的漫画读者？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 235016, "content": "不会主动去看漫画，但在公众号、微博里碰到新的条漫都会看一看", "image": "img/option/option/201709121738435LWcHgG2DzxIs0qe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235018, "content": "关注专门漫画app和网站，时不时也会看看漫画直播", "image": "img/option/option/20170912174206mUKbPNoFIh3jfM2k.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235022, "content": "碰到动画精彩就会去看漫画原作，动画进度慢也会转向漫画", "image": "img/option/option/20170912174827sPgt9liVOnREDqCf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235023, "content": "只追经典漫，翘首以盼海贼王、猎人之类的更新", "image": "img/option/option/20170912174948qpZKMv7DuWHlnCPA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235024, "content": "关注了一些漫画大V，很喜欢篇幅短的场景漫画", "image": "img/option/option/20170912175600Wt28hrnKuRXHjoNI.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235025, "content": "漫画书爱好者，看漫画果然还是在纸上更有味道", "image": "img/option/option/20170912175918v1JQeGO0RIWUdt6p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235026, "content": "国漫支持者，常去国内原创漫画网站，国漫好作品越来越多", "image": "img/option/option/20170913162438PhHFQv1M6OIYnlae.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235027, "content": "深度研究员，动漫的历史、知识也很让人振奋", "image": "img/option/option/20170912180432JjkTA6fraboRsuYF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235215, "content": "美漫迷，美漫成熟，有不少发人深省的犀利吐槽和好故事", "image": "img/option/option/20170913163309sbxW5PtMwjaOiTDv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 235217, "content": "基本不看，日常离漫画最近的就是表情包了，吧", "image": "img/option/option/20170913163939qlgaFGbrVKyB0hDL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}